      simp [hr‚āĀ]
    rw [this]
    simp [hr‚āĀ]
    -- We need to ensure that 1/r is not ‚ąě, which is true since r ‚Č† 0
    -- The expression (1 / r : ‚ĄĚ‚Č•0‚ąě) is equal to (1 / r : ‚ĄĚ) because r ‚Č† 0
    -- And (1 / r : ‚ĄĚ) is finite, so it's not ‚ąě
