```

Now we can prove the Cauchy-Schwarz inequality:

```tactics
/-- **Cauchy-Schwarz inequality** -/
lemma wInner_cWeight_le_cL2Norm_mul_cL2Norm (f g : őĻ ‚Üí ‚ĄĚ) : ‚ü™f, g‚üę‚āô_[‚ĄĚ] ‚Č§ ‚ÄĖf‚ÄĖ‚āô_[2] * ‚ÄĖg‚ÄĖ‚āô_[2] := by
  simp only [wInner_cWeight_eq_smul_wInner_one, cL2Norm_eq_expect_nnnorm, ‚Üź NNReal.coe_mul, expect,
